      "text": [
        "576 - وَقَالَ اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ: «كُلُّمَا جُعِلَ عَلَى اَلْقَبْرِ مِنْ غَيْرِ تُرَابِ اَلْقَبْرِ فَهُوَ ثِقْلٌ عَلَى اَلْمَيِّتِ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.576 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said:\n\"Whatever is placed on the grave that is not from the soil of the grave itself is a burden upon the deceased.\""
        ]
      }
    },
